OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 11 MAY
OL,4,G2200FThe Sky at Night
OL,5,     GThe team explore the remarkable
OL,6,     Gstory of Jodrell Bank Observatory
OL,7,     Gand its towering Lovell
OL,8,     GTelescope, which scientists have
OL,9,     Gused to listen to the cosmos for
OL,10,     Galmost 70 years.
OL,11,G2230FBritish Art at War: Bomberg,
OL,12,     FSickert and Nash
OL,13,     GAndrew Graham-Dixon tells the
OL,14,     Gstory of David Bomberg, the
OL,15,     Gstartlingly original British
OL,16,     Gpainter who died in obscurity
OL,17,     Gover 50 years ago.
